{"tid":1540791,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港澳辦中聯辦與習近平打擂台","createTime":"2019-09-04T12:33:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T12:51:13.000Z","uid":68822,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4710b2b827c132badbc8a1ed9ba5eb8bbf23ba15","tid":1540791,"uid":68822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:33:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkepochfans/videos/351060049104830/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkepochfans%2Fvideos%2F351060049104830%2F&d=HFtALxS4LzZAkeshXsvvbqix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=f034f7a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkepochfans/videos/351060049104830/</a><br />\n<br />\n呢排一直同朋友討論有關中共習派同江派高層內鬥<br />\n結論大約都係講中共入面有唔少人不滿習近平<br />\n想借香港局勢升溫而拉習近平下台<br />\n同呢條片入面所分析嘅局勢差唔多<br />\n好清楚指出現時香港權力同中共高層關係<br />\n解釋左中共、港府、中聯辦、港澳辦背後所反映出黎嘅習/江鬥爭<br />\n未必一定全中，但可以Share比啲淺黃等佢地更了解現時局勢"},{"pid":"85dd9b2e7f0274734c55d62d08f1a7fa543f446a","tid":1540791,"uid":68822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:34:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40eb7abeb895ae6a9d3f9547e2028dcdfda2695e","tid":1540791,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:38:29.000Z","msg":"summer be water<br />\n我地再次睇 烏克蘭 既懶人包<br />\n香港人 動起來<br />\n柒婆既一次又一次謊言只係昆鳩港豬<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GmN4glJK80I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DGmN4glJK80I&d=HFtALxS4LzZAkeshXsvvbqix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=d457f0e0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GmN4glJK80I</a>"},{"pid":"dd1a229c38559ccec200d68f63e56c5493ace744","tid":1540791,"uid":68822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:51:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}